Cell.Data: This model is representative of our fictional company: MobileCord Inc.
You may use this model as the basis for your own, or just use it as a point of reference.
Our Model is made up of the following worksheets:
Worksheets from "Employees" to "Service Expenses" define the expense side of the business.
Worksheets From "Pipeline Assumptions" to "Revenue" define the Revenue side of the business
Worksheets "Monthly P&L" to "Cap Table" are the financial statements that VCs and investors will want to see.
Investors will probably also want to see the pipeline.

Worksheets "Bal Sheet for Offer Memo" through "P&L summ for Offer Memo" are copies of the Balance Sheet and Quarterly P&L sheets in order to format these statements for the presentation in the offering memorandum.
